title: qeema naan
description:
INGREDIENTS:

Lamb mince                      1 kg
onion                                  1 medium size
Cilantro                              50 g 
Garlic chopped                 2 tbsp 
Ginger                                2 tbsp
Green chilies                     3-4
Coriander seeds               2tbsp
Cumin                                2 tbsp
Red chili powder              2 tsp
Cardamom powder         1 tsp
salt                                     to taste

ingredients for the dough 

water                                    100 ml
 sugar                                   1 tbsp
 active dry yeast                  7g
All-purpose flour                 500g
Salt                                        3tsp
Yogurt                                   100 ml
Vegetable oil                        2 tbsp
Water                                    150 ml
